text: The Klagenfurt-Land District (German: Bezirk Klagenfurt-Land, Southern Austro- Bavarian: Beziak Klognfuat-Laund) is a district in the state of Carinthia in Austria. The capital is Klagenfurt. == Municipalities == Towns (Städte) are indicated in boldface; market towns (Marktgemeinden) in italics; suburbs, hamlets and other subdivisions of a municipality are indicated in small characters.
